1- download and install the latest DirectX from Microsoft.com (or from a recent game CD)

2- download and install C++ package from
http://www.microsoft.com/downloads/details.aspx?familyid=32BC1BEE-A3F9-4C13-9C99-220B62A191EE&displaylang=en

3- Unrar, run setup.exe, and use provided serial number.
